# 1. Start with a ride script

You can easily compile ride scripts using the [waves-ide](https://waves-ide.com/)
```
{-# STDLIB_VERSION 3 #-}
{-# CONTENT_TYPE DAPP #-}
{-# SCRIPT_TYPE ACCOUNT #-}

@Callable(i)
func callBack() = {
  let lastNumberOfUpdates = match getInteger(this, "updates") {
		case p:Int => p
		case _ => 0
	}
  ScriptResult(
    WriteSet([
    DataEntry("updates", lastNumberOfUpdates + 1)
    ]),
    TransferSet([
      ScriptTransfer(i.caller, 100000000, base58'5ih9jd4KV9kSey55yvKMgLSHcwsYYkQ4pRDJtRNoxUhy')
    ]))
}

@Callable(i)
func incrementData() = { 
  let lastNumberOfUpdates = match getInteger(this, "updates") {
		case p:Int => p
		case _ => 0
	}
  WriteSet([DataEntry("updates", lastNumberOfUpdates + 1)])
}

@Verifier(tx)
func verify() = sigVerify(tx.bodyBytes, tx.proofs[0], tx.senderPublicKey)
```
